@node Introduction

As nobody would have expected from the title :) , these are some new block sets
for the game @{i}Pairs@{ui} by Tobias Lenz. Some of them are a bit more difficult to
play, others are (IMHO) easier than the original set. So there should be at
least one suitable for highscore hunters as well as for people looking for a
challenge. Give 'em a try!

@endnode

